			Company Description 
		


                Sigma Designs, Inc. engages in the provision of media platforms for home entertainment. It develops, manufactures, and sells media processors, smart televisions, power line, and wired media connectivity. The company was founded by Thinh Q. Tran in 1982 and is headquartered in Fremont, CA.
            




